## Modal Props

- `id`: Unique identifier (auto-generates `{id}-content` for content wrapper)
- `zIndex`: Z-index for backdrop (content gets zIndex + 1)
- `blurAmount`: "none" | "sm" | "md" | "lg" | "xl"
- `opacity`: String like "50" for 0.50 opacity
- `mobileOnly`: Boolean for mobile-only display
- `backdropClasses`: Additional classes for backdrop
- `contentClasses`: Additional classes for content wrapper

## Benefits

- Consistent appearance across app
- Centralized backdrop styling
- Automatic z-index management
- Blur and opacity control
- Slot-based content (clean and intuitive)
- Easier maintenance
